---
alwaysApply: true
---

Rust conventions for this project:

- Domain entities must be immutable when possible.
- Business invariants must be enforced in constructors.
- Use traits for ports.
- Infrastructure provides implementations.

Crate structure:

domain/
application/
infrastructure/
ui/

Domain must contain:

- entities
- value objects
- aggregates
- domain events
- repository traits
